snippet.title: Stick Stunt Biker - v6.1
snippet.description: Bike fun and challenging tracks using your destructible stick biker including jumps, loopings, fire and other funny obstacles. Stick Stunt Biker is an agil and fast physic based bike game, with new updates every few weeks. (Stick Stunt Biker has seen more than 26 updates already and is played by more than 15 million players).
